id: "class:fighter#two_weapon_warrior"
name: "Two-Weapon Warrior"
description: "Trained under great masters who preached the simple truth that two are\
  \ better than one when it comes to weapons, the two-weapon warrior is a terror when\
  \ his hands are full. From paired daggers to exotic double weapons, all combinations\
  \ come equally alive in his skilled hands."
